' Связи между классами

StorageHouse -left--> DocWorks
StorageHouse -right---> Item
DocWorks o---left iDoc
iDoc<|..Acception
iDoc<|..Order
Acception *---right AcceptItem
AcceptItem -up--> Item
DocWorks -left--> iReposDoc
iReposDoc <|..-down docRepos
StorageHouse -right-->iReposStor
StorageHouse -right-->iStorage
iStorage <|.. StockCell
iStorage <|.. StorageComposit
StorageComposit o-up-> iStorage
StorageComposit *---down StockShelf
StorageComposit *---down StockRoom
iReposStor<|..-down storRepos
@enduml
